<div id="review_1694189788" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1694189788" />
    <a title="Prabhjot Kaur" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/52645070-prabhjot-kaur"><img alt="Prabhjot Kaur" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1623719881p2/52645070.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1694189788?book_show_action=true">Jul 10, 2016</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Prabhjot Kaur" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Prabhjot Kaur" href="/user/show/52645070-prabhjot-kaur">Prabhjot Kaur</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9781681443133" href="/book/show/29776085-secret-of-the-nagas">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/52645070-prabhjot-kaur?shelf=indian">indian</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/52645070-prabhjot-kaur?shelf=indian-author">indian-author</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/52645070-prabhjot-kaur?shelf=historical-fiction">historical-fiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/52645070-prabhjot-kaur?shelf=mythology">mythology</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/52645070-prabhjot-kaur?shelf=fiction">fiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/52645070-prabhjot-kaur?shelf=hindu-mythology">hindu-mythology</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1694189788" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3932363755937563068">I have said this before and I will say it again that Amish Tripathi&apos;s imagination knows no bounds. He&apos;s one of the most imaginative Indian authors. But once again I didn&apos;t end up loving the book, once again I wanted to.<br/><br/>It&apos;s thrilling, we even have some really great twists in the story but I felt like something was amiss. May be because the original depiction that we have of Lord Shiva and Ganesha is beyond perfect. I went into reading this with a clean slate and still I was disappointed. May be </span>
  <span id="freeText3932363755937563068" style="display:none">I have said this before and I will say it again that Amish Tripathi's imagination knows no bounds. He's one of the most imaginative Indian authors. But once again I didn't end up loving the book, once again I wanted to.<br /><br />It's thrilling, we even have some really great twists in the story but I felt like something was amiss. May be because the original depiction that we have of Lord Shiva and Ganesha is beyond perfect. I went into reading this with a clean slate and still I was disappointed. May be it's my fault that I set my expectations too high even though I didn't much like The Immortals of Meluha. It's definitely on me.<br /><br />It wasn't completely terrible but I was expecting more. I still look forward to the next book in the series.<br /><br />3 stars</span>
  <a data-text-id="3932363755937563068" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


